      Subinterfaces of ResourceWriteCallback in de.adorsys.datasafe.types.api.callback 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      interface  PhysicalVersionCallback
      Called when file is persisted on storage that supports versioning natively to tell callee what was the version id assigned to the file (happens when OutputStream is closed and response from storage is received).
      interface  SoftwareVersionCallback
      Called when file is persisted using software-versioning to tell callee what was the version id assigned to the file (happens when OutputStream is closed and response from storage is received).
